            "default_value": "The Port St Mary Commissioners are committed to serving our community with transparency, integrity and care. Our mission is to support local needs, maintain essential services and help Port St Mary thrive as a vibrant seaside village.\r\nWe work collaboratively with residents, local organisations and stakeholders to deliver services that reflect the values and priorities of our community. Through open communication and responsible stewardship, we aim to build trust and strengthen community engagement.\r\nOur focus is on maintaining public spaces, supporting local initiatives and ensuring that decisions are made in the best interests of those who live, work and visit Port St Mary. We are dedicated to listening, responding and acting with accountability at all times.",
